</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>Be of no misconception 
</span><span class='line'>another death has spawned a generation.
</span><span class='line'>We are children of a moment
</span><span class='line'>wide-eyed at the prospect of living
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>where cotton picked euphoria will take on the law
</span><span class='line'>where legality will be left glancing forward,
</span><span class='line'>craning its neck to see, darting forth,
</span><span class='line'>straining against the red tape, and watching
</span><span class='line'> 
</span><span class='line'>the leader of the race turn and laugh,
</span><span class='line'>stare in bemusement at their futility, shrug
</span><span class='line'>as a new burst of energy is released 
</span><span class='line'>into the clubs, onto the streets, into the valleys and the schools, 
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>the floodgates have opened,
</span><span class='line'>evolving with open source pharmacology,
</span><span class='line'>to a discarded generation disgusted with propaganda 
</span><span class='line'>rejoicing a ride into rebellion</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>

